    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S (996.2) is a superlative example of the wide-body chassis, featuring a meticulously maintained 3.6L flat-six engine with VarioCam Plus. The M96 powerplant has undergone a documented IMS bearing retrofit and shows zero evidence of bore scoring. Power is delivered through a crisp G96 6-speed manual transaxle to a sophisticated viscous-coupling AWD system. The chassis remains exceptionally tight, benefiting from refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, while the Turbo-spec four-piston monobloc calipers provide fade-free deceleration. Finished in concours-level Arctic Silver over Graphite Grey leather, this C4S retains its factory-fresh tactile feedback and mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
