      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and the original factory scent remains. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assistance features, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is perfect, accompanied by a comprehensive service portfolio with all preventative maintenance performed ahead of schedule by certified technicians. The undercarriage is exceptionally clean, reflecting its history as a fair-weather-only driver. This is a turn-key, investment-grade example that satisfies even the most detail-oriented collector.",
